  <section id="tabulator">
  <paragraph id="hd_id3148668" role="heading" level="1" oldref="1" l10n="U" xml-lang="en-US"><link href="text/shared/02/13010000.xhp" name="Setting Tabs">Setting Tabs</link></paragraph>
  <paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3154873" l10n="U" xml-lang="en-US" oldref="2">On the ruler, set the tabs for the current paragraph, or all selected paragraphs, using the mouse.</paragraph>
  </section>
  <paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3148520" l10n="U" xml-lang="en-US" oldref="3">Initially the default tabs are shown on the horizontal ruler. Once you set a tab, only the default tabs to the right of the tab that you have set are available.</paragraph>
  <embed href="text/shared/guide/tabs.xhp#tabs"/>
